    "UIName": "Seishin",
    "Id": "chassisdef_seishin_SN-X4",
    "Name": "Seishin",
    "Details": "The Seishin SN-X4 is a 50-ton pirate-built BattleMech assembled from post-Jihad Word of Blake salvage and black market components in the Tortuga Dominions. A right-torso BattleMech Taser fed by two CASE-protected tons of ammunition serves as the primary weapon, designed to immobilize targets for capture rather than destruction. A right-torso ER Large Laser provides ranged reach, while a left-arm Shield, right-arm Retractable Blade, and left-torso laser array complete a close-range package built around recovering intact salvage.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_seishin"
  },
  "VariantName": "SN-X4",
